B.KC=new A.bd(B.bT,["Director Oslo","Accord Attach\xe9","official","Commander. Your mission parameters are clear \u2014 reach Accord Prime and deliver the xenodata payload. Do not deviate from the approved route."],t.l)
B.Ky=new A.bd(B.bT,["Director Oslo","Accord Attach\xe9","official","The crew roster includes Civic Accord observers. Their reports go directly to High Command. I trust you understand what that means."],t.l)
B.HA=s([B.KC,B.Ky],t.SN)
B.Kx=new A.bd(B.bT,["Commander Tesh","Fleet Liaison","commander","You made it through the inner corridor. Word of warning \u2014 the Accord's communication blackout in Sector 3 isn't a technical fault. Something out there is jamming our signals."],t.l)
B.Hw=s([B.Kx],t.SN)
B.KA=new A.bd(B.bT,["Quartermaster Pol","Supply Corps","trader","Commander. Sigma Relay stocks are limited but I can move product. Credits talk out here \u2014 AccordNet requisitions don't get answered fast enough to matter."],t.l)
B.Hy=s([B.KA],t.SN)
B.Ku=new A.bd(B.bT,["Salvager Moxen","Independent Trader","trader","Nice ship. Shame about the war. You're headed to Keth'ari space? They don't shoot first, Commander. That's not what the Accord tells you, but I've been working this field a long time."],t.l)
B.Hu=s([B.Ku],t.SN)
B.KB=new A.bd(B.bT,["Envoy Shiral","Keth'ari Speaker","alien","[ Resonance field coalesces into meaning ] ...You carry pain, Commander. Your crew carries more. We do not wish this war. But we will not be extinguished quietly."],t.l)
B.KD=new A.bd(B.bT,["Envoy Shiral","Keth'ari Speaker","alien","[ The resonance deepens ] ...Ask your Accord why the Solune migration ended. Ask what they found in the Graveyard. The answer changes everything."],t.l)
B.Hz=s([B.KB,B.KD],t.SN)
B.Kz=new A.bd(B.bT,["Admiral Cress","Accord Navy","commander","You made it through the Reach. Good. Accord Vanguard is the last friendly port before the final push. Stock up if you're able \u2014 Accord Prime won't wait."],t.l)
B.Hx=s([B.Kz],t.SN)
B.Kv=new A.bd(B.bT,["High Director Vale","Accord Command","official","You've arrived. The Accord thanks you for your service, Commander. The xenodata you've gathered will determine the next phase of the campaign."],t.l)
B.Kw=new A.bd(B.bT,["High Director Vale","Accord Command","official","What you discovered in Keth'ari space must not leave this chamber. The public narrative of this war is... fragile. Do you understand, Commander?"],t.l)
B.Hv=s([B.Kv,B.Kw],t.SN)
